    echo -e "${C1}┣━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┫${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}01${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}INSTALAR / REINSTALAR V2RAY${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}02${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}AGREGAR USUARIO${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}03${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}LISTAR USUARIOS${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}04${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}ELIMINAR USUARIO${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}05${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}VER CONFIG (URI VLESS / VMess)${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}06${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}CAMBIAR PUERTOS V2Ray${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}07${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}CONFIGURAR TLS + NGINX (opcional)${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}08${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}ESTADO Y SERVICIOS${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}09${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}REINICIAR XRAY${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}10${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}REINICIAR / ACTIVAR NGINX${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}11${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}DETENER XRAY${NC}"
    echo -e "  ${C2}|${C3}12${C2}|${NC}➜ ${C4}DESINSTALAR${NC}"
